campaign.story:
// ABOUT THE PROJECT
The Persian Empire (ROYAL EDITION) is a continuation of The Persian Empire (ORIGINAL) playing cards. The Cards are designed based on the Persian Empire using detailed artwork. The cards are branded by Bicycle and manufactured by USPCC. The Royal Road map will be printed by The Half and Half printing company.
The cards are designed based on the ancient Persian empire. They are numbered both in Persian & English. The kings, queens and jacks are based on the royal family.
I've created varieties of pledges to show my gratitude for your help and support. There is also an Add-on Price Sheet which you can find on this page. If you would like to add any item to your pledge, please see the appropriate price and add the amount to your pledge. For international backers, there is a shipping price which you can find on the same sheet. Domestic shipping is free.
// SAMPLE CARDS
// THE ROYAL ROAD MAP
5 color screen print with a special finish. The poster's dimension is 24"x18".
// ABOUT THE MAP
The Royal Road map is wall art of the Persian Empire and it's Royal Road which connected the empire from Europe to Asia. It extended 1677 miles (2699 km).
// MAKING OF THE ROYAL ROAD MAP
 // PERSIAN EMPRE MAP BANDANA
1 color screen printed 22"x22" bandana
// ADD-ON PRICE SHEET
// PREVIOUS PROJECT
The Persian Empire (Original) has been printed and shipped to all my previous backer on December 2013.
